{"tid":877200,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"香港只有7大","createTime":"2018-10-26T07:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T04:50:03.000Z","uid":137521,"like":705,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"e82bb315322a709aff04faf6d8ec917bfbbdc222","tid":877200,"uid":137521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:18:57.000Z","msg":"浸會中學呢d垃圾讀黎都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n辱校罪都諗得出，班學校高層冇得救架啦<br />\n<br />\n排名又係咁跌，出到國際都係當野雞大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反正政府又認可其他私立大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁點解仲要讀浸中呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入浸會悔終身，OU恒管更稱心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n建議DSE廿分頭既人唔好再揀浸中，浸中個名只會越黎越臭，不如去其他私立大學或者做後門狗入返7大算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當DSE廿分頭都唔入浸中，入晒其他私立大學，係不久既將來僱主自然會知呢間專出廢物，到時其餘私立大學既名氣點都好過浸中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前上一輩都覺得ust差過poly，最後ust咪又係好地地變左做三大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要俾連登仔日日吹捧為亞洲MIT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話唔定到時OU變埋八大呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15522033844adb356dd849689074eb5ced896efd","tid":877200,"uid":200153,"like":18,"dislike":163,"score":-145,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:21:33.000Z","msg":"點都好過LingU呱⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471aba0177f312aef22f7b2cb019715b0d5df0a2","tid":877200,"uid":137521,"like":319,"dislike":4,"score":315,"quote":{"pid":"15522033844adb356dd849689074eb5ced896efd","tid":877200,"uid":200153,"like":18,"dislike":163,"score":-145,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:21:33.000Z","msg":"點都好過LingU呱⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:22:17.000Z","msg":"LingU假假地都叫大學<br />\n點都好過浸中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd346301c7f6e70c47e8ef66402ff863edc88721","tid":877200,"uid":36296,"like":5,"dislike":89,"score":-84,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:28:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/26/152846_7e72aca773b52117ff5890c0da99c7d4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F26%2F152846_7e72aca773b52117ff5890c0da99c7d4.png&h=cac83d1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f0aa64d5b373e15b1bd2ad645a2974126f17a6","tid":877200,"uid":137521,"like":196,"dislike":5,"score":191,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:29:52.000Z","msg":"下一屆既預自己得廿分頭既DSE考生<br />\n勸你哋都係唔好再以為岩岩好入到浸中就打晒飛機<br />\n以為自己係大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲早你哋出到黎揾工個陣<br />\n個hr知道你浸中出黎之後直接screen走你張cv<br />\n因為到時大家普遍認知都係浸中呢d垃圾入面既人dse連廿分都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc0a4636387dcc38c5a68d5ae0f588f6fc0e875","tid":877200,"uid":137521,"like":70,"dislike":12,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:33:41.000Z","msg":"DSE廿分頭既人不如諗下入左ou恒管點樣屈下GPA仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nOU first hon點都好聽過浸中畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d67830daca34c406a8962a47d162248459becc2","tid":877200,"uid":137521,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:35:49.000Z","msg":"如果入左浸中，諗起遲d畢業見工俾隔離d ou恒管仔指住黎笑就覺得慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32543296c0a162d3203965946fe1802c2698b17","tid":877200,"uid":137521,"like":63,"dislike":2,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:39:17.000Z","msg":"第時入到浸中，一下唔覺意吐兩句苦水，轉個頭俾人踢返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5ecfb07b0644acef4048d2d20018c978110764","tid":877200,"uid":137521,"like":77,"dislike":5,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:41:18.000Z","msg":"到時同支那人開片，再俾d支那人投訴兩下，又唔使講證據，讀讀下就俾人話影響校譽踢出校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad18c74450cf0d3f6df6c2badb8dddc45ae08e1","tid":877200,"uid":175032,"like":198,"dislike":2,"score":196,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:51:03.000Z","msg":"認真浸大依家真係仲衰過lingu"},{"pid":"22bce04cf8879506495313e43c19a0f66809cbef","tid":877200,"uid":137521,"like":135,"dislike":8,"score":127,"quote":{"pid":"dad18c74450cf0d3f6df6c2badb8dddc45ae08e1","tid":877200,"uid":175032,"like":198,"dislike":2,"score":196,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:51:03.000Z","msg":"認真浸大依家真係仲衰過lingu"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T08:11:24.000Z","msg":"lingU d人俾我既印象都真係幾好<br />\n好文青feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n浸中過多幾年應該變成垃圾先會想入"},{"pid":"ffddf2a67031eb76b3879f68203c6ef668ec9bd4","tid":877200,"uid":175598,"like":121,"dislike":59,"score":62,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T08:19:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08791406990b96a0c37f7c0d40e09698c12ad981","tid":877200,"uid":200516,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"ffddf2a67031eb76b3879f68203c6ef668ec9bd4","tid":877200,"uid":175598,"like":121,"dislike":59,"score":62,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T08:19:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:15:49.000Z","msg":"想同埋土囝開戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339dca2223585ca386fdaa726b94ba0a65ea62f9","tid":877200,"uid":209270,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"ffddf2a67031eb76b3879f68203c6ef668ec9bd4","tid":877200,"uid":175598,"like":121,"dislike":59,"score":62,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T08:19:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:19:46